<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٤٨ ... سُورَةُ الفَتْحِ ... آياتها ٢٩ مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتْحًا مُّبِينًا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هُوَ:</span> صُلْحُ الحُدَيْبِيَةِ عَامَ سِتٍّ مِنَ الهِجْرَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صِرَاطًا مُّسْتَقِيمًا}</span> ... طَرِيقًّا، وَدِينًا لَا عِوَجَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَزِيزًا}</span> ... قَوِيًّا لَا ضَعْفَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّكِينَةَ}</span> ... الطُّمَانِينَةَ، وَالثَّبَاتَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيُكَفِّرَ}</span> ... يَمْحُوَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ظَنَّ السَّوْءِ}</span> ... الظَّنَّ السَّيِّئَ؛<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span> الظَّنُّ بِأَنْ لَنْ يَنْصُرَ اللهُ دِينَهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَيْهِمْ دَائِرَةُ السَّوْءِ}</span> ... دُعَاءٌ عَلَيْهِمْ بِأَنْ تَدُورَ عَلَيْهِمْ دَائِرَةُ العَذَابِ، وَكُلُّ مَا يَسُوءُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَصِيرًا}</span> ... مَنْزِلًا يَصِيرُونَ إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتُعَزِّرُوهُ}</span> ... تَنْصُرُوا اللهَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتُوَقِّرُوهُ}</span> ... تُعَظِّمُوا اللهَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُكْرَةً وَأَصِيلًا}</span> ... أَوَّلَ النَّهَارِ، وَآخِرَهُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَّكَثَ}</span> ... نَقَضَ بَيْعَتَهُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُخَلَّفُونَ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ تَخَلَّفُوا عَنِ الخُرُوجِ مَعَكَ إِلَى مَكَّةَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْأَعْرَابِ}</span> ... البَدْوِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّن يَنقَلِبَ}</span> ... لَنْ يَرْجِعَ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>